amendment.description: An amendment numbered 7 printed in House Report 118-428 to codify Florida's Clean Water Act Section 404 Program and the Programmatic Biological Opinion with Incidental Take Statement, as referenced in 85 Federal Register 83,553 (December 22, 2020).

vote.text: On agreeing to the Bean (FL) amendment (A006) Agreed to by voice vote.

action.text: House amendment agreed to: On agreeing to the Bean (FL) amendment (A006) Agreed to by voice vote.
